Youngster Benson Omalla came in for Ulimwengu as Gor upped the tempo in search of the lead.He nearly scored after Muguna curved a free kick inside the six-yard box, but his shot went inches wide. A brace by Gor Mahia forward Tito Okello ensured reigning champions Gor Mahia moved to the eighth position in Football Kenya Premier League standings after beating Western Stima 3-1 in a Betking Premier League match on Monday.
The match held at Kisumu's Moi Stadium was physical from the start with every player going for the other’s jugular.



