Okello was not done yet, a pass from Omalla would find him in a good position and after a few dribbles past defenders, he scored with a shot at the bottom left corner.
Gor Mahia now moves to eighth in the log, with nine points, but have played only five matches compared to league leaders KCB’s seven.  Mathare's coach Salim Ali was elated with the win. Tusker seem to be getting back on track. The 32-year-old man said he had been directed to sacrifice a girl, goat and a chicken and surrender the hearts so that he could be protected from his relatives “who were planning to kill him”. The city has seen a second wave after authorities relaxed some restrictions. Ms Mwenda is now facing an acid test that could dim her quest to become the first female governor of Nairobi.